pr_title: Add covariant return types to methods in MultiReaderList that return `this`.

timeline.message:
Add covartiant return types to methods in MultiReaderList that return `this`.

Signed-off-by: Craig P. Motlin <cmotlin@gmail.com>

timeline.bodyText: This needs to be protected by a call to withWriteLockAndDelegate.
